: scene manager
- controls drawable entities
  - sprites (correspond to physics entities)
  - background
- has a 'focus' entity, which it keeps in view of camera

:physics manager
- controls physics entites
  - sprites (correspond to drawable entities)
  - walls (screen boundaries)

:drawable entity
  - getImage()
  - getPosition()

:physics entity
  - size
  - position
  - velocity
  - acceleration
